# Ration Terminology Glossary

One term, one meaning, everywhere across the codebase:

- **Hub** — The main authenticated layout/home page. Not "Dashboard".
- **Cargo** — The inventory management section and its items. Not "Pantry" or "Inventory".
- **Galley** — The meal planning section/page. Not "Meals page".
- **Meal** — A single cookable recipe with ingredients. Not "Recipe".
- **Ingredient** — A component of a Meal (references a Cargo item). Use only in meal context.
- **Supply** — The shopping list section. Not "Grocery".
- **Supply List** — A shopping list. Not "Grocery list".
- **Supply Item** — An entry on a supply list. Not "Grocery item".
- **Item** — Generic, acceptable in context (e.g., "Add Item" on Cargo page).
